                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-center text-white bg-blue-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 sm:w-auto dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 dark:focus:ring-blue-800">Đăng nhập </button>
                    <div class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
